body_html: What Pete is saying is that once your app is built it should compress. It's similar with the android app when you quantise. It shows as full size but once built in it compresses. Try putting it the app and then analysing for size to see if it's compressed as @petewarden suggested.

body: What Pete is saying is that once your app is built it should compress. It's similar with the android app when you quantise. It shows as full size but once built in it compresses. Try putting it the app and then analysing for size to see if it's compressed as @petewarden suggested.
